Summary: 
 * Decoupled free space available tokens checking
   from token consumption and production.
 - Removed getAvailableSpace and getAvailableTokens
 - Added   getFreeSpace      and getConsumableTokens which
   replace getAvailableSpace and getAvailableTokens but
   have different semantics. They no longer imply token
   consumption or production
 - Token consumption are now specified only via
   inXX(...) and outXX(...).
